task.summary: basic GUI with hooks for the database
Basic sign up form (person details) is done
Added new classes to Storage package. Started implementing the StorageFacade. Added some exception classes.
Finished implementing (I think so..). Need to add unit tests.
Finished providing Logic Facade with Storage Facade that supports it.

Added function getLoggedUser(String username), which returns a User object representing the currently logged user. This function can replace checkIfUserExists(String username) becasue it uses it to determine if the user exists in the database.
Changed functions that throw exceptions unrelated to FrontEnd. Changed functions return value, so that FrontEnd wont have to face exceptions that don't relate to it.
